<L>__{interior sawyer's restaurant late morning.}
<A>__{sethe enters late, putting on her apron as sawyer yells;}
<C>__{sawyer}
<D>__{what the hell you thinking, girl? strolling in here this late?}
<C>__{sethe}
<D>__{don't talk to me, mr. sawyer. don't say nothing to me this morning.}
<C>__{sawyer}
<D>__{what? what? you talking back to me?}
<C>__{sethe}
<D>__{i'm telling you don't say nothing to me.}
<A>__{sethe begins organizing her counter to make pies.}
<C>__{sawyer}
<D>__{you better get them pies made!}
<A>__{sethe ignores him as she begins. sawyer is at a loss.}
<C>__{sawyer}
<D>__{not too sweet! you make it too sweet they don't eat it.}
<C>__{sethe}
<D>__{make it the way i always do.}
<C>__{sawyer}
<D>__{yeah. too sweet.}
<P>__{(he exits)}
